===Other symbols===
<gallery widths="100px">
File:Bi triangles.svg|[[Biangles]]<br />(represents Bisexuality)
File:Bisexual-moon-symbol.svg|[[Bisexuality#Symbols|Double moon]]<br />(represents Bisexuality)
